{"tid":1893593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老實講香港廢老真係好驚死!!","createTime":"2020-02-23T11:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T11:10:28.000Z","uid":119688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8944eb18a9e25cb0c9f55e46cc81d46db2da3cc2","tid":1893593,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:07:41.000Z","msg":"出街見d阿叔勁撚重裝<br />\n心諗洗唔洗咁驚<br />\n識好多連工都唔返門都唔出<br />\n到底廢老個腦諗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明旺區根本無影響<br />\n人照樣多 食既買既香港人一樣照比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢老真係好垃圾 <br />\n利申:屋企有個垃圾廢老煙鏟<br />\n嚇到街都唔出<br />\n好似人地以前吸鴉片果彈咁<br />\n足不出戶 訓係度成日吸毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d5f08c78ff7613e1cccef5acfa1b2b12428ea0","tid":1893593,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}